Copyright (c) 2026 Bradley Buchsbaum.
License: MIT (the amatrix.opencl package license).
These small umbrella headers are authored by the amatrix project. They redirect
the <CL/opencl.h> / <OpenCL/opencl.h> includes used by clblast_c.h to the
vendored Khronos core C API headers, so the extension headers (cl_gl.h,
cl_ext.h) that the package does not use are not required.
